                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.4112/73: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schoenfeld</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-06-14T13:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 14, 1924—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>304. Embassy’s 212 dated June 13, 11 a.m. If Mexican Government should violate
                    British Legation the Department authorizes you to join with the diplomatic corps
                    in a protest should that body determine upon such action.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
